snippet.title: Rusty Lake Paradise Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Jakob, the oldest son of the Eilander family, is returning to Paradise island after his mother passed away. Since her mysterious death, the island seems to be cursed by the ten plagues. Find the mother's hidden memories and partake in strange family rituals in order to stop the plagues.

Rusty Lake Paradise is the third premium point-and-click adventure by Rusty Lake, the creators of the Cube Escape series, Rusty Lake Hotel & Rusty Lake: Roots.

Rusty Lake Paradise is now available on:
iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id1253855339
Google Play:  https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=air.com.RustyLake.RustyLakeParadise
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/744190/Rusty_Lake_Paradise/
Itch.io: https://rustylake.itch.io/rusty-lake-paradise

Like and follow:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/rustylakecom
Twitter: https://twitter.com/rustylakecom
Instagram: https://instagram.com/rustylakecom/
And subscribe to our mailing list: http://eepurl.com/bhphw1

Special thanks to:
Victor Butzelaar: http://www.victorbutzelaar.com/ (Soundtrack)
Bob Rafferty: http://www.bobrafferty.co.uk/ (Trailer & Voice-over)
